description: Cold treats for hot peeps are here, Houston! We are NOT your typical ice cream truck! We serve 100% non-fat, Gluten Free, Non-dairy fruit shell sorbets and Italian Ices; Authentic Italian Ice, Gourmet Ice cream Truffles, Handmade Ice Cream Sandwiches, Thick & tasty shakes; Handmade small batch ice creams, Gourmet ice cream truffles; Crazy yummy sundaes; Poppin' & rockin' sno-cones; Fabulous floats; and other sweet surprises...You won't forget us after your first sweet experience, we're sure it won't be your last! Making Houston sweeter..one cold, yummy treat at a time!
name: SweetRide! Houston Dessert Truck
